sequenceDiagram
    box rgb(245,245,245) Create Competition
        actor Organizer as Tournament Organizer
        participant UI as Competition Management UI
        participant Auth as Permission Evaluation
        participant CLS as Competition Lifecycle Service
        participant CDA as Category and Division Administration
        participant DB as Persistence Layer

        Organizer->>UI: Create competition
        UI->>Auth: Check permission
        Auth-->>UI: Allowed
        UI->>CLS: Create competition draft
        CLS->>CDA: Configure categories and divisions
        CDA-->>CLS: Categories and divisions configured
        CLS->>DB: Save competition
        DB-->>CLS: Competition persisted
        CLS-->>UI: Competition created
    end

    box rgb(245,245,245) Register and Approve Participant
        actor Player
        actor Organizer2 as Tournament Organizer
        participant UI2 as Registration Management UI
        participant RRS as Registration Review Service
        participant DB2 as Persistence Layer

        Player->>UI2: Submit registration
        UI2->>RRS: Create registration
        RRS->>DB2: Save registration as pending review
        DB2-->>RRS: Registration persisted
        RRS-->>UI2: Registration recorded

        Organizer2->>UI2: Review registration
        UI2->>RRS: Approve or reject registration
        RRS->>RRS: Validate category and division alignment
        RRS->>DB2: Update registration status
        DB2-->>RRS: Registration updated
        RRS-->>UI2: Reviewed registration state
    end

    box rgb(245,245,245) Generate Competition Structure
        actor Organizer3 as Tournament Organizer
        participant UI3 as Competition Management UI
        participant CPS as Competition Structure / Progression Service
        participant DB3 as Persistence Layer

        Organizer3->>UI3: Generate competition structure
        UI3->>CPS: Build structure from approved registrations
        CPS->>DB3: Read approved registrations by category and division
        DB3-->>CPS: Approved participant set
        CPS->>CPS: Create bracket, draw, or fixture structure
        CPS->>DB3: Save matches and progression structure
        DB3-->>CPS: Structure persisted
        CPS-->>UI3: Competition structure ready
    end

    box rgb(245,245,245) Record Match Result
        actor Staff as Competition Support Staff
        participant UI4 as Match & Result Operations UI
        participant RVS as Result Validation Service
        participant CPS2 as Competition Structure / Progression Service
        participant DB4 as Persistence Layer

        Staff->>UI4: Record match result
        UI4->>RVS: Submit result
        RVS->>DB4: Save result as recorded
        DB4-->>RVS: Result stored
        RVS->>RVS: Validate result
        alt Result valid
            RVS->>CPS2: Advance progression
            CPS2->>DB4: Update match progression and derived outcomes
            DB4-->>CPS2: Progression updated
            CPS2-->>RVS: Progression advanced
        else Result invalid
            RVS-->>UI4: Result remains unresolved
        end
        RVS-->>UI4: Result state returned
    end

    box rgb(245,245,245) Close Competition
        actor Manager as Club Competition Manager
        participant UI5 as Competition Operations Dashboard
        participant CCS as Competition Closure Service
        participant DB5 as Persistence Layer

        Manager->>UI5: Close competition
        UI5->>CCS: Request closure
        CCS->>DB5: Check registrations, matches, and results
        DB5-->>CCS: Competition state snapshot
        CCS->>CCS: Verify operational completeness
        CCS->>DB5: Mark competition completed and finalize outcome
        DB5-->>CCS: Competition closed
        CCS-->>UI5: Closure confirmed
    end
